- How long was that?
- He was unconscious.

13
00:04:39,653 --> 00:04:41,112
He wasn't aware of any pain.

14
00:04:41,321 --> 00:04:42,948
How long, Doctor?

15
00:04:43,615 --> 00:04:45,325
Twenty minutes.

16
00:04:51,957 --> 00:04:54,417
- Have you ordered x-rays?
- They're on their way.

17
00:04:56,002 --> 00:04:58,880
She'll need an urgent CT scan.

18
00:05:00,632 --> 00:05:02,551
Decerebrate response?

19
00:05:02,968 --> 00:05:04,386
It's her husband.

20
00:05:07,889 --> 00:05:09,808
I want you to talk to her.

21
00:05:14,646 --> 00:05:16,189
Rae, it's John.

22
00:05:21,778 --> 00:05:23,113
Try it again.

23
